  %% Diagram 22A: Payment and Escrow Business-Friendly Journey

  Start([Buyer places an order]) --> Method{Choose payment method}

  Method --> Pay[Buyer pays via bKash/Nagad/SSLCommerz/Bangla QR/Rocket]
  Pay --> Verified{Payment verified?}

  Verified -- No --> Retry[Show retry or alternate payment options]
  Retry --> Method

  Verified -- Yes --> Hold[Funds moved to escrow - Held]
  Hold --> Ship[Vendor fulfills and ships the order]
  Ship --> Delivered{Order delivered?}

  Delivered -- No --> Support[Support follows delivery issue workflow]
  Delivered -- Yes --> Satisfied{Buyer satisfied or no dispute in 48h?}

  Satisfied -- Yes --> Release[Escrow released to vendor]
  Release --> Payout[Vendor payout processed]

  Satisfied -- No --> Dispute[Claim review - Disputed state]
  Dispute --> Outcome{Claim decision}
  Outcome -- Buyer wins --> Refund[Refund buyer from escrow]
  Outcome -- Vendor wins --> Release

  Payout --> Audit[All transitions logged in audit trail]
  Refund --> Audit
  Support --> Audit
